  <body>
    <br />
    <h1>Welcome to my demo website</h1>
    <h3>This site illustrates Cheq's core capabilities</h3>

    <hr />
    
    <h4>Homepage RTI Response</h4>
    <pre><span><%- rtiResString %></span></pre>

    <div class="tabs">
      <button class="tab-button" onclick="openTab(event, 'tab1')">
        Defend (RTI)
      </button>
      <button class="tab-button" onclick="openTab(event, 'tab2')">
        Form Guard (SLP)
      </button>
    </div>
    <br />
    <br />
    <br />
    <div id="tab1" class="tab-content">
      <h2>CHEQ Defend</h2>
      <p>Clicking the Subscribe button takes you to the Subscribe page.</p>
      <p>
        UNLESS - you are an invalid visit. In that case you will be redirected
        to a custom url ü§ñüëãüèº
